::Primal Prime::

    "As of now, you can call me Prime. Things are still being sorted out 
inside my head." Prime said. "What I need to talk to you about is the Maximal 
Matris of Leadership. I need to know some important things."
    Prime looked into Hot Rod's optics. "That happened to you? You really 
should be questioning wether I am Optimus Prime or in reality a Predacon."
